<div id="txtcont" class="span9" style="position: relative;">
    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='157:183'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-1a' );" name="004-1a" class="pb">[004-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='183:191'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='191:202'>　周易章句證異卷四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='202:223'>　　　　　　　　　　　内閣中書翟均廉撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='223:228'>彖下傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='228:251'>　胡瑗作下彖二程逈作彖下二吕祖謙朱子作彖下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='251:260'>　傳二餘見上傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='260:265'>咸感也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='265:288'>柔上而剛下二氣感應以相與止而説男下女是以亨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='288:314'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-1b' );" name="004-1b" class="pb">[004-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='314:322'>利貞取女吉也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='322:345'>天地感而萬物化生聖人感人心而天下和平觀其所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='345:358'>感而天地萬物之情可見矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='358:380'>恆久也剛上而柔下雷風相與巽而動剛柔皆應恆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='380:403'>恆亨无咎利貞久於其道也天地之道恆久而不已也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='403:432'>　荀爽作恆亨无咎<span class='krp-note'>句吳澄/  同</span>孔頴逹作恆亨无咎利貞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='432:439'>　<span class='krp-note'>句/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='439:450'>利有攸徃終則有始也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='450:476'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-2a' );" name="004-2a" class="pb">[004-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='476:502'>　陸時位以利有攸徃二句接久於其道也<span class='krp-note'>云照/古本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='502:525'>日月得天而能久照四時變化而能久成聖人久於其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='525:547'>道而天下化成觀其所恆而天地萬物之情可見矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='547:570'>　陸時位以天地之道二句移置此之首云此節古本</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='570:583'>　在文言下後人附入彖傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='583:600'>遯亨遯而亨也剛當位而應與時行也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='600:609'>小利貞浸而長也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='609:618'>遯之時義大矣哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='618:644'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-2b' );" name="004-2b" class="pb">[004-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='644:657'>大壯大者壯也剛以動故壯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='657:677'>大壯利貞大者正也正大而天地之情可見矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='677:705'>　陸時位以正而大天地之情可見矣别為一節<span class='krp-note'>云古/本在</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='705:720'>　<span class='krp-note'>文言中後人/附入彖傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='720:725'>晉進也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='725:748'>明出地上順而麗乎大明柔進而上行是以康侯用錫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='748:758'>馬蕃庶晝日三接也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='758:766'>明入地中明夷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='766:792'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-3a' );" name="004-3a" class="pb">[004-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='792:809'>　俞琰曰或以明入地中為衍文非也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='809:826'>内文明而外柔順以蒙大難文王以之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='826:855'>　毛竒齡曰李鼎祚無而字作内文明外柔順<span class='krp-note'>廉案李/本有而</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='855:885'>　<span class='krp-note'>字不知毛/何所據</span>　以之鄭𤣥荀爽向秀作似之下同　王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='885:908'>　肅作惟文王能用之下同　陸時位以内文明而外</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='908:929'>　柔順移利艱貞晦其明也下<span class='krp-note'>云照/古本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='929:949'>利艱貞晦其明也内難而能正其志箕子以之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='949:972'>家人女正位乎内男正位乎外男女正天地之大義也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='972:998'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-3b' );" name="004-3b" class="pb">[004-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='998:1011'>家人有嚴君焉父母之謂也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1011:1034'>父父子子兄兄弟弟夫夫婦婦而家道正正家而天下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1034:1038'>定矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1038:1058'>　陸時位曰此節古本在文言後人附入彖傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1058:1078'>暌火動而上澤動而下二女同居其志不同行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1078:1101'>説而麗乎明柔進而上行得中而應乎剛是以小事吉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1101:1125'>天地暌而其事同也男女暌而其志通也萬物暌而其事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1125:1136'>類也暌之時用大矣哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1136:1162'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-4a' );" name="004-4a" class="pb">[004-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1162:1184'>　陸徳明曰此節古本在文言下後人附入彖傳中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1184:1201'>蹇難也險在前也見險而能止知矣哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1201:1224'>蹇利西南徃得中也不利東北其道窮也利見大人徃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1224:1244'>有功也當位貞吉以正邦也蹇之時用大矣哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1244:1263'>　邦陸績作國<span class='krp-note'>案陸徳明/為漢朝諱</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1263:1275'>解險以動動而免乎險解</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1275:1298'>解利西南徃得衆也其來復吉乃得中也有攸徃夙吉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1298:1304'>徃有功也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1304:1330'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-4b' );" name="004-4b" class="pb">[004-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1330:1353'>　其來復吉上李鼎祚有无所徃三字<span class='krp-note'>惠棟/同</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1353:1376'>天地解而雷雨作雷雨作而百果草木皆甲拆解之時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1376:1381'>大矣哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1381:1418'>　拆馬融鄭𤣥荀爽陸績作宅<span class='krp-note'>云宅根也作惠棟作宅/云宅古文  □□字壊</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1418:1432'>　<span class='krp-note'>而為拆作/拆者訛也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1432:1443'>損損下益上其道上行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1443:1466'>損而有孚元吉无咎可貞利有攸徃曷之用二簋可用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1466:1488'>享二簋應有時損剛益柔有時損益盈虚與時偕行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1488:1514'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-5a' );" name="004-5a" class="pb">[004-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1514:1533'>益損上益下民説无疆自上下下其道大光</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1533:1551'>利有攸徃中正有慶利渉大川木道乃行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1551:1590'>　木道程子改作益道<span class='krp-note'>朱子曰不須改孚俞琰曰以渙/之乗木有功中  之乗木舟虚</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1590:1602'>　<span class='krp-note'>準之宜/從朱子</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1602:1625'>益動而巽日進无疆天施地生其益无方凡益之道與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1625:1630'>時偕行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1630:1645'>夬決也剛決柔也健而説決而和</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1645:1658'>　郭京曰此下脱乃亨二字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1658:1684'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-5b' );" name="004-5b" class="pb">[004-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1684:1707'>揚于王庭柔乗五剛也孚號有厲其危乃光也告自邑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1707:1727'>不利即戎所尚乃窮也利有攸徃剛長乃終也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1727:1736'>姤遇也柔遇剛也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1736:1747'>勿用取女不可與長也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1747:1775'>　郭京曰勿用上脱女壯字勿用取下誤增女字<span class='krp-note'>毛竒/齡云</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1775:1782'>　<span class='krp-note'>誤/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1782:1793'>天地相遇品物咸章也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1793:1804'>剛遇中正天下大行也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1804:1830'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-6a' );" name="004-6a" class="pb">[004-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1830:1839'>姤之時義大矣哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1839:1854'>萃聚也順以説剛中而應故聚也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1854:1877'>王假有廟致孝享也利見大人亨聚以正也用大牲吉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='1877:1887'>利有攸徃順天命也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='1887:1910'>　享毛居正曰字宜作亨誤作享　王昭素曰亨屬上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='1910:1944'>　句<span class='krp-note'>王輔嗣云通聚以正/以亨字連下句非也</span>　郭京曰聚以正上脱利貞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='1944:1972'>　二字　九家易李鼎祚作聚以正下有利貞字<span class='krp-note'>毛竒/齡云</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='1972:2001'>　<span class='krp-note'>謬/</span>　荀爽作取以正<span class='krp-note'>晁說之曰取古/文毛竒齡云誤</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2001:2027'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-6b' );" name="004-6b" class="pb">[004-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2027:2043'>觀其所聚而天地萬物之情可見矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2043:2064'>　陸時位曰此節古本在文言中後人附入彖傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2064:2070'>柔以時升</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2070:2083'>巽而順剛中而應是以大亨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2083:2102'>　程子曰元亨誤作大亨<span class='krp-note'>俞琰/從之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2102:2119'>用見大人勿恤有慶也南征吉志行也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2119:2125'>困剛揜也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2125:2157'>　揜荀爽虞翻李鼎祚作弇<span class='krp-note'>晁説之曰弇古/文  惠棟同</span>陸徳明曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2157:2183'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-7a' );" name="004-7a" class="pb">[004-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2183:2191'>　揜本又作掩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2191:2214'>險以説困而不失其所亨其惟君子乎貞大人吉以剛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2214:2227'>中也有言不信尚口乃窮也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2227:2265'>　龍仁夫作困而不失其所<span class='krp-note'>句梁寅葉良佩查慎行同/    毛竒齡曰當以所句</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2265:2282'>　<span class='krp-note'>句郎覬引此/  不連亨字</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2282:2297'>巽乎水而上水井井養而不窮也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2297:2320'>　范諤昌作巽乎木而上水　郭京曰井養而不窮下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2320:2326'>　脱亨字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2326:2352'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-7b' );" name="004-7b" class="pb">[004-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2352:2375'>改邑不改井乃以剛中也汔至亦未繘井未有功也羸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2375:2383'>其瓶是以凶也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2383:2406'>　李鼎祚作改邑不改井乃以剛中也无喪无得徃來</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2406:2428'>　井井汔至亦未繘未有功也井羸其瓶是以凶也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2428:2451'>　朱震作巽乎水而上水井改邑不改井乃以剛中也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2451:2474'>　无䘮无得徃來井井井養而不窮也汔至亦未繘井</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2474:2503'>　未有功也井羸其瓶是以凶也<span class='krp-note'>云疑彖/傳脱簡</span>　郭京曰改</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2503:2533'>　邑不改井下脱无䘮无得徃來井井二句<span class='krp-note'>徐氏晁説/之王昭素</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2533:2559'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-8a' );" name="004-8a" class="pb">[004-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2559:2587'>　<span class='krp-note'>蔣悌/生同</span>　惠棟汔至亦未繘井上增无䘮无得徃來井</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2587:2593'>　井二句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2593:2611'>革水火相息二女同居其志不相得曰革</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2611:2639'>　水火相息晁説之曰兑无為水之象此字必誤<span class='krp-note'>古今/无人</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2639:2653'>　<span class='krp-note'>辯/者</span>　息許慎作熄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2653:2676'>已日乃孚革而信之文明以説大亨以正革而當其悔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2676:2680'>乃亡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2680:2696'>　革而信之陸徳明曰一本无之字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2696:2722'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-8b' );" name="004-8b" class="pb">[004-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2722:2745'>天地革而四時成湯武革命順乎天而應乎人革之時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2745:2750'>大矣哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2750:2771'>　陸時位曰此節古本在文言中後人附入彖傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2771:2794'>鼎象也以木巽火亨飪也聖人亨以享上帝而大亨以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2794:2799'>養聖賢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2799:2826'>　亨飪聖人亨大亨三亨字陸徳明曰本又作□<span class='krp-note'>普庚/切</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2826:2855'>　<span class='krp-note'>晁説之曰/□古文</span>　陸時位亨如字訓通云先儒改亨為亨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='2855:2878'>　武斷過矣　毛居正曰享上帝釋文亨香兩反今作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='2878:2904'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-9a' );" name="004-9a" class="pb">[004-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='2904:2939'>　享誤<span class='krp-note'>俞石澗曰古者亨烹享通/作亨改亨為享今文也</span>　郭京作聖人亨以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='2939:2972'>　亨上帝以養聖賢<span class='krp-note'>云誤增而大亨字二陸時/位曰古本无大亨  字</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='2972:2995'>巽而耳目聰明柔進而上行得中而應乎剛是以元亨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='2995:2999'>震亨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='2999:3017'>震來虩虩恐致福也笑言啞啞後有則也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3017:3055'>　吳澄曰无此十六字<span class='krp-note'>云彖詞重出初九爻詞故後人/於彖傳亦重引初九象傳以釋</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3055:3068'>　<span class='krp-note'>之宜衍之/季本從</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3068:3091'>震驚百里驚遠而懼邇也出可以守宗廟社稷以為祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3091:3117'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-9b' );" name="004-9b" class="pb">[004-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3117:3121'>主也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3121:3154'>　郭京曰出字上脱不喪匕鬯四字<span class='krp-note'>徐氏王昭素歐陽/修晁説之朱震晁</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3154:3193'>　<span class='krp-note'>公武王宗傳朱子鄭汝/諧王申子俞琰諸儒同</span>虞翻王弼无不䘮匕鬯字<span class='krp-note'>石/介</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3193:3234'>　<span class='krp-note'>張子吕大臨趙彦肅項安世李舜臣梁/寅鄭維岳陳仁錫查慎行皆不從郭京</span>朱子曰出字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3234:3260'>　或即鬯字之誤<span class='krp-note'>吳澄增不䘮匕鬯/四字  季本同</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3260:3283'>艮止也時止則止時行則行動靜不失其時其道光明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3283:3306'>　陸時位曰時止則止古本在文言中後人增入　郭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3306:3319'>　京曰光明下脱故亨二字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3319:3346'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-10a' );" name="004-10a" class="pb">[004-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3346:3369'>艮其止止其所也上下敵應不相與也是以不獲其身</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3369:3381'>行其庭不見其人无咎也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3381:3404'>　陸以艮止也三字移冠節首　晁説之曰止當依卦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3404:3447'>　詞作背<span class='krp-note'>云古本无艮其止之説王弼妄為之説虞翻/軰何得无一言盖是時尚未錯誤也項安世</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3447:3495'>　<span class='krp-note'>曰古文背字為北有訛為止字之理朱熊過從之陸/時位云古文作背今文誤  二程子  子俱作艮其</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3495:3502'>　<span class='krp-note'>止/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3502:3512'>漸之進也女歸吉也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3512:3548'>　朱子曰之字疑衍或是漸字<span class='krp-note'>呉澄曰因寫下漸字作/二因遂訛為之  晉王</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3548:3575'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-10b' );" name="004-10b" class="pb">[004-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3575:3607'>　<span class='krp-note'>本作漸云以漸/重文二故誤之</span>　呉澄删之字　郭京曰吉下誤增</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3607:3647'>　也<span class='krp-note'>晁説之曰虞/翻亦无也字</span>　王肅作女歸吉利貞<span class='krp-note'>李心傳從王/本  呉澄删</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3647:3666'>　<span class='krp-note'>也字增/利貞字</span>程子諸儒俱如字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3666:3674'>其位剛得中也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3674:3683'>止而巽動不窮也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3683:3706'>歸妹天地之大義也天地不交而萬物不興歸妹人之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3706:3711'>終始也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3711:3729'>　陸時位曰此節係文言後儒增入彖傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3729:3756'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-11a' );" name="004-11a" class="pb">[004-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3756:3765'>説以動所歸妹也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3765:3792'>　所歸妹也陸徳明作所以歸妹也<span class='krp-note'>晁説之曰/作所以非</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3792:3807'>征凶位不當也无攸利柔乗剛也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3807:3817'>豐大也明以動故豐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3817:3829'>　故豐林栗曰當作故亨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3829:3847'>王假之尚大也勿憂宜日中宜照天下也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='3847:3870'>日中則昃月盈則食天地盈虚與時消息而况于人乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='3870:3877'>况于鬼神乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='3877:3904'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-11b' );" name="004-11b" class="pb">[004-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='3904:3937'>　昃孟喜作稷<span class='krp-note'>晁説之曰/稷古文</span>　食陸徳明曰或作蝕非<span class='krp-note'>晁/説</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='3937:3948'>　<span class='krp-note'>之曰蝕/俗字</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='3948:3971'>旅小亨柔得中乎外而順乎剛止而麗乎明是以小亨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='3971:3977'>旅貞吉也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='3977:4008'>　呉澄曰柔得上小亨二字衍<span class='krp-note'>俞琰曰或両言小/亨其一疑衍非也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4008:4017'>旅之時義大矣哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4017:4024'>重巽以申命</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4024:4055'>　郭京曰命下脱命乃行也四字誤入註<span class='krp-note'>徐氏王昭素/晁説之朱震</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4055:4082'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-12a' );" name="004-12a" class="pb">[004-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4082:4108'>　<span class='krp-note'>從/之</span>　朱震曰巽為命先儒謂不違其令命乃行也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4108:4131'>　陸時位以兑卦是以順乎天而應乎人句接重巽以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4131:4154'>　申命云二句古本在文言後人附入彖傳又將是以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4154:4162'>　句割裂兌卦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4162:4185'>剛巽乎中正而志行柔皆順乎剛是以小亨利有攸徃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4185:4191'>利見大人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4191:4196'>兌説也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4196:4219'>剛中而柔外説以利貞是以順乎天而應乎人説以先</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4219:4246'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-12b' );" name="004-12b" class="pb">[004-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4246:4268'>民民忘其勞説以犯難民忘其死説之大民勸矣哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4268:4291'>　陸時位曰是以順乎天而應乎人句宜在巽卦申命</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4291:4300'>　句下古本可証</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4300:4317'>渙亨剛來而不窮柔得位乎外而上同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4317:4328'>王假有廟王乃在中也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4328:4339'>利渉大川乗木有功也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4339:4369'>　郭京曰利渉大川脱利貞二字<span class='krp-note'>王申子曰不及/利貞疑有逸文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4369:4380'>節亨剛柔分而剛得中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4380:4407'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-13a' );" name="004-13a" class="pb">[004-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4407:4419'>　俞琰曰中下欠一也字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4419:4430'>苦節不可貞其道窮也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4430:4444'>説以行險當位以節中正以通</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4444:4471'>　郭京曰中正以通下有然後乃亨也一句誤入注<span class='krp-note'>毛/竒</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4471:4502'>　<span class='krp-note'>齡曰以後人注/木增經文誤</span>　陸時位以説以行險三句移剛柔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4502:4524'>　分而剛得中句下<span class='krp-note'>云後人亂之/今復古本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4524:4543'>天地節而四時成節以制度不傷財不害民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4543:4563'>　陸時位曰此節古本作文言後人附入彖傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4563:4590'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-13b' );" name="004-13b" class="pb">[004-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4590:4609'>中孚柔在内而剛得中説而巽孚乃化邦也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4609:4622'>　李鼎祚以説而巽孚斷節</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='4622:4641'>豚魚吉信及豚魚也利渉大川乗木舟虚也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='4641:4669'>　郭京曰豚魚吉信及也今本誤增豚魚二字<span class='krp-note'>毛竒齡/曰謬</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='4669:4679'>小過小者過而亨也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='4679:4689'>過以利貞與時行也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='4689:4700'>柔得中是以小事吉也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='4700:4735'>　郭京作是以可小事也<span class='krp-note'>云以下脱可字事下/誤增吉字  俞琰同</span>　石經</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='4735:4762'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-14a' );" name="004-14a" class="pb">[004-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='4762:4799'>　云是以可小事也<span class='krp-note'>項安世曰彖辭脱可字羡吉/字  程逈從石經  呉澄同</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='4799:4814'>剛失位而不中是以不可大事也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='4814:4837'>有飛鳥之象焉飛鳥遺之音不宜上宜下大吉上逆而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='4837:4842'>下順也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='4842:4865'>　程子曰有飛鳥之象焉句不類彖體解者之詞誤入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='4865:4901'>　彖中<span class='krp-note'>毛竒齡云呉仁傑偽造古易/隂承程傳之意遂去此句</span>　俞琰曰或謂大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='4901:4922'>　吉之大亦衍文<span class='krp-note'>盖承彖辭傳/寫之誤也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='4922:4931'>既濟亨小者亨也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='4931:4958'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-14b' );" name="004-14b" class="pb">[004-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='4958:4981'>　孔頴逹曰文當更有一小字但既叠經文畧足以見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='4981:5023'>　故從省也<span class='krp-note'>項氏安世曰孔頴逹謂當作既濟亨小小/者亨也盖脱一小字廉案項説與正義不</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='5023:5055'>　<span class='krp-note'>同晁説之亦云孔/謂合有両小字</span>　郭京曰亨小小者亨也下脱一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='5055:5087'>　小字<span class='krp-note'>朱震/同</span>　晁説之曰既濟小亨小者亨也<span class='krp-note'>朱本義/從之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='5087:5110'>　<span class='krp-note'>熊良輔胡一桂胡炳/文同  餘説見彖辭</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='5110:5121'>利貞剛柔正而位當也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='5121:5144'>　毛竒齡曰李鼎祚本作當位則與亨終窮韻不恊非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='5144:5161'>　是廉案今李本亦作位當與毛説異</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='5161:5188'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '004-15a' );" name="004-15a" class="pb">[004-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='5188:5196'>初吉柔得中也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='5196:5206'>終止則亂其道窮也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='5206:5215'>未濟亨柔得中也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='5215:5238'>小狐汔濟未出中也濡其尾无攸利不續終也雖不當</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='5238:5245'>位剛柔應也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='5245:5248'>　</span><br/>
